<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Fatty Fitness</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: url(https://img.freepik.com/fotos-premium/3d-rendering-schwarze-hanteln-auf-dem-boden-im-dunklen-konzeptfitnessraum-mit-trainingsausruestungen-im-ruecken_67155-14961.jpg); }
        header { background: #dd2222; color: #fff; padding: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
        nav { background: #444; padding: 10px 0; }
        nav a { color: #fff; margin: 0 15px; text-decoration: none; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 30px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; }
        h1, h2 { margin-top: 0; }
        .features { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; }
        .feature { flex: 1 1 250px; background: #eee; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; }
        footer { background: #222; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 15px 0; margin-top: 40px; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .features { flex-direction: column; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Gym Owner App</h1>
        <p>Manage your gym, members, trainers, and schedules with ease!</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="#">Members</a>
        <a href="#">Trainers</a>
        <a href="#">Classes</a>
        <a href="#">Settings</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome, Gym Owner!</h2>
        <p>This app helps you manage your gym efficiently. Track memberships, trainers, class schedules, and more.</p>
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Member Management</h3>
                <p>Add, edit, or remove gym members. Track attendance and payments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Trainer Management</h3>
                <p>Assign trainers to classes, manage their schedules and profiles.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Class Scheduling</h3>
                <p>Create and manage fitness classes, set timings, and enroll members.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Reports & Analytics</h3>
                <p>View reports on membership growth, revenue, and attendance trends.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Gym Owner App. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>